  "Description": {
    "English": "A defensive crimson cocoon, obfuscating the ship's physical form and providing protection from collision and laser fire.<br><br>The core self-heals over time, but may be quickly replenished with <span class=\"name name-catalyst\">catalytic elements</span> or <span class=\"name name-special\">radiant shards</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于防御的猩红色茧，能够遮蔽飞船的物理形态并提供针对撞击与激光攻击的保护。<br><br>核心能够缓慢自我再生，但同时也能够通过<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">催化元素</span>或<span class=\"name name-special\">光耀碎片</span>快速恢复。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一種防禦性緋紅色繭袋，可模糊太空船的實體外型，提供碰撞及雷射砲火防護。<br><br>核心會隨時間自我修復，不過也可以使用<span class=\"name name-catalyst\">催化元素</span>或<span class=\"name name-special\">發光裂片</span>快速修復。"
  },
